autoMerging.description: A block that specifies the configuration about the auto-merging process. Documented below.

enabled.description: The flag that enables the matching process of duplicate profiles.

exportingConfig.description: A block that specifies the configuration for exporting Identity Resolution results. Documented below.

jobSchedule.description: A block that specifies the day and time when you want to start the Identity Resolution Job every week. Documented below.
